---
title: Quick Coconut & Makrut Lime Chicken Curry with Garlic Rice & Baby Corn Spears
description: Tonight's dinner is a superb infusion of aromatics and substance. Here, we’ve doubled up on superstar
ingredients, with fragrant garlic in the rice so it smells and tastes like a tropical holiday, plus an addition of makrut lime leaves in the curry for a delicious touch of citrus.
